==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 27|''Star Wars'' (1977) 27]] {{C|Part 3}}
*"The power of Warlock Part 8: How strange my destiny! Part 2: Redemption principle!"
*"Micronauts Part 6: The prometheus pit!" (Continuation)
*"Tales of the Watcher: Last warning: Evacuate Earth!"

